name: Paisley Cuff
description:
This design has been a long time in coming. My Paisley Ring has been so popular, that I decided to try it in a cuff.

http://www.etsy.com/view_listing.php?listing_id=33586203

It's now my favorite piece and I have one in my personal collection that I wear practically every day! I love it! Hope you do too!

Bracelet: Handmade from shrink plastic, leather cord and sterling silver chain.
Approximate Dimensions:
Plastic face: 2 3/4" x 1 1/2"
Length: Adjustable from 5 3/4" - 7 1/2"

All jewelry is sealed with a clear acrylic waterproof sealer. Although they have been waterproofed, keep them dry to stay in tip-top shape. Each item is handmade and therefore, totally unique. Item may vary slightly from the photo.
